					<div id="ppcollapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="ppheadingOne" data-bs-parent="#patientPolicies">
					  <div class="accordion-body">
						<p>If your appointment is between 8:00 AM and 11:00 AM, and you are over the age of 19, please fast 10-12 hours prior to your appointment. You may have water, black coffee or unsweet tea. Drink lots of water prior to your visit. Please arrive 10-15 minutes early to allow us adequate check-in time. Remember to bring your insurance card and driver’s license to the appointment. If you need to cancel or reschedule, please provide a 24-hour notice or you will be charged for a missed appointment. Also, please remember to print and complete the Review of Systems form and bring it with you to your appointment.</p>
					  </div>
